long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you want to see Francis Bourgeois everywhere, you've come to the right place! This plugin will turn all images on any website (and some supported videos) to images of Francis Bourgeois. The perfect prank for a train spotter.

This plugin should work in most websites, and can easily be disabled from the plugins menu.

Francis Bourgeois is a well known viral train spotter in the United Kingdom, who has featured on train spotting TV series as well as being TikTok famous.
